{"tid":1859360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[HK01] 武肺死亡率低，兼有得醫！！！","createTime":"2020-02-03T08:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T08:42:32.000Z","uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5a35ba07c300261a009c0aeaec0f6020f07e27f6","tid":1859360,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T08:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e379ab04e64212bb85ad5f9.jpg/xo6JI2znJsrvynMDGo8JJHRsWGZFYLoXzO31Yczt9WE?v=w960r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e379ab04e64212bb85ad5f9.jpg%2Fxo6JI2znJsrvynMDGo8JJHRsWGZFYLoXzO31Yczt9WE%3Fv%3Dw960r16_9&h=061e80e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國武漢於2019年年底爆發新型冠狀病毒肺炎，由於目前尚無特效藥，再加上謠言的傳播，一些民眾產生了恐慌心理。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞衛生部1月31日在Twitter上澄清：肺炎患者不會變成喪屍。<br />\n<br />\n衛生部在社交媒體上分享了三個關於新型冠狀病毒肺炎的事實：患者不會變成喪屍；患者可以被治癒，應與普通發燒區分；目前致死率在2%到3%左右，較SARS（約10%）、中東呼吸綜合症（約34%）來說其實很低。<br />\n<br />\n截至2月3日，馬來西亞已確診8名輸入型患者，均接受隔離。<br />\n<br />\n此外，馬來西亞衛生部呼籲民眾不要發布或傳播謠言，因為此舉會危害國家安全。"},{"pid":"47a634f17ab1495b5e0e50c628fb7eb91d7deb9e","tid":1859360,"uid":91432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T08:09:38.000Z","msg":"1995年美國電影《血疫》"},{"pid":"d49339a40783ef50edfa2fc09d9116e85681edb9","tid":1859360,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T08:10:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42abbf177dff8d257fdff1dbaea7cedc35162d3c","tid":1859360,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T08:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c62317a46513e5b4dce4caa15408555f673bdb","tid":1859360,"uid":90328,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T08:11:14.000Z","msg":"當媒體叫你唔好恐慌時 你係時候要擔心了"},{"pid":"1c103e952e07f7e1a1f6e9a18587f1ffbb19737c","tid":1859360,"uid":221265,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T08:11:28